    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      For anyone who will participate in colon screening at the Princess Grace Hospital of Monaco&#xD;
      and who has signed the informed consent document. A blood test will be performed in addition&#xD;
      to the screening test to assess the rate of progastrin.&#xD;
    </textblock>
